AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_000414> "The sexual functions, activities, attitudes, and orientations of an individual."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_000414> "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Sexuality"^^xsd:anyURI)
