AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_000699> "https://sexuality.fandom.com/wiki/Asexuality"^^xsd:anyURI)
