# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_000700> (allosexuality)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_000700> "The condition of being allosexual (in any of its many senses)."@en)
