AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GSSO_004911> "Sexuality in which a person can be aroused by sexual material (such as pornography) and who participates in sex acts like masturbation, but otherwise has no interest in having a sexual partner or external sexual interactions."@en)
